# Architecture

**Scope:** Better Auth `auth` schema in core only — no product Prisma domains in shared dashboard `lib/`. Features = removable subtrees.

**Deps:** sub-feature → segment `lib/` → `src/lib` \| `src/components`. No cross-sibling feature imports.

**Action-first:** colocate `app/<segment>/` + matching `app/action/<segment>/` (one mutation per file).

**SSOT:** `*-routes.ts`, `cache-tags.ts` per segment.

**Before new code:** search upward; inline by default — [architecture.md § Placement](docs/agents/architecture.md#placement).

**Detail (Read):** [docs/agents/architecture.md](docs/agents/architecture.md).
